libs.content:
find_program(_clang_tidy
    names clang-tidy-7 clang-tidy-6.0 clang-tidy-5.0 clang-tidy-4.0 clang-tidy
    doc "path to clang-tidy executable")

find_library( bolt_library_static_release
        names libclbolt.runtime.gcc.a
        hints
            ${bolt_root}
            env bolt_root
        doc "bolt static library path"
        path_suffixes lib
    )

find_library( bolt_library_static_debug
        names libclbolt.runtime.gcc.debug.a
        hints
            ${bolt_root}
            env bolt_root
        doc "bolt static library path"
        path_suffixes lib
    )

find_library(tbb_library tbb hints ${_tbb_library_dir}
        paths env library_path env ld_library_path)

find_library(tbb_malloc_library tbbmalloc hints ${_tbb_library_dir}
        paths env library_path env ld_library_path)

find_library(tbb_library_debug tbb_debug hints ${_tbb_library_dir}
        paths env library_path env ld_library_path)

find_library(tbb_malloc_library_debug tbbmalloc_debug hints ${_tbb_library_dir}
        paths env library_path env ld_library_path)
